or.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-225x300.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 225w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-800x1067.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-90x120.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 90w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-768x1024.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-1152x1536.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1152w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-696x928.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-1068x1424.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/17085332/hope-hb-tt-front-view-8-cm-wide-fork-seat-stay-blades-315x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 315w\"></a></p><p>First off, why? The Hope HB.TT started off as nothing more than a fun idea off the back of a conversation with one of Hope Technology’s owners, Ian Weatherill. While car manufacturer Lotus was a key partner in the creation of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/10/31/hope-hb-t-x-lotus-3d-printed-ti-carbon-track-bike-is-british-cyclings-wild-olympic-secret-weapon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Team GB’s Olympic Track Bike</a>, the HB.TT is entirely a Hope creation. <em>“We wanted to make the track bike a bit more user friendly with a few gears and a set of brakes so we could use the bike we had made!”</em> – Sam Pendred, Designer of the HB.TT.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"hope hb.tt headtube woven carbon time trial bike aerodynamic\" width=\"1200\" height=\"745\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-297x184.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-800x497.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-768x477.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-696x432.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-1068x663.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-677x420.jpg 677w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-356x220.jpg 356w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-297x184.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-800x497.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-768x477.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-696x432.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-1068x663.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-677x420.jpg 677w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102116/hope-hb-tt-time-trial-bike-aerodynamic-geometry-356x220.jpg 356w\"></a></p><p>Not ones to sit idly and wait for the world to return to normality, Sam and the Hope designers used the quiet time during the pandemic to develop a first prototype, which is what you see here; a bike that has prototype approval from the UCI. The carbon used in the prototype frame is the same high modulus material Hope used for the track bike, said to be the highest performing material that Hope use.</p><figure id=\"attachment_268213\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-268213\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon.jpg\" alt=\"hope hb.tt wild looking aerodynamic time trial bike seat tube stay junction\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102043/hope-hb-tt-aero-time-trial-bike-carbon-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/