rumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/16102049/hope-hb-tt-carbon-aerodynamic-time-trial-bike-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a>Can I have one?</h3><p>Not yet. Yet, being the operative word. <em>“We are currently looking into ways that will reduce the cost of the bikes so we can offer them at a much more affordable price. With unavoidable complexity in some of the custom components and the desire to maintain the grade of carbon used in the Olympic bikes, we think it may be in the region of £10,000 to £15,000”</em> – Sam Pendred.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>HopeTech.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"49247959d93d06f6353c15787b5cec88ab3a37c9e075ab6988d4a632f48c2c9f","category":"Cycling"}